            "resource": {
                "@type": "dctypes:Text",
                "format": "text/html",
                "chars": "<p>It is not possible to definitively determine who among the committee tasked with revising The Sacred Harp contributed to this \"Preface.\" The preface's writing style resembles James's, but it is noteworthy that the attribution diverges from that for the \"Introductory\" section, where James is credited as sole author.</p>",
                "language": "en"
            },
